Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] The current Kira is foolish\Nand overconfident,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,not to mention unusually cooperative\Nwith the Task Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.21,0:01:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I suspect he's working\Nhand in hand with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-You think so?\N-That would make the second L and Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,one and the same person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-[monitor beeping]\N-[Near] To the members
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Japanese Task Force...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there ever a point\Nin the investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,where the second L\Nwas suspected to be Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,even if the suspicion was later dropped?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Near... I have to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting] This is really bad!\NTurn on the TV! It's Demegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Demegawa, live.\NMy comrades and I have finally pinpointed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the hideout of the evil organization\Nbent on trying to catch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-our beloved god, Kira.\N-[mob yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We now have the building\Ncompletely surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,TRANSFER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[tires screeching]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[jingle playing on TV]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] Fellow Kira supporters,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I urge you, do not rush the building\Nall at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The traitors may attempt to blend in\Nwith the crowd to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Kira's loyal servant and spokesman.\NYou must listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Find them, move them from the building,\Nand bring them in front of the cameras!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-They'll be a sacrifice to Kira!\N-[glass cracking]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[mob yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hide from me. I'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Near, you've got no choice.\NYou better evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve to say that,\Nbeing Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you still going on\Nabout that nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it.\NWith all the anti-Kira groups around,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.60,0:03:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,why is it we're being targeted,\Nand right after I start suspecting you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty convenient, if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Near, with all due respect,\Nyou're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're jumping to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Members of the Task Force,\Nplease listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira is likely amongst you.\NEven as we speak, he is in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm simply asking you\Nto think about this carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] "Light is Kira."\NThis is all sounding way too familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The original L also thought\Nthat Light had to be Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[mob yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The first wave of 20 people\Nwill break the door and get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-Second wave, stand by!\N-[man grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the way, idiot!\NWe're the first wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Like hell! We're going first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-Near, we have to evacuate immediately.\N-[glass shattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Really, what pathetic people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not surprised\Nthat there are ordinary people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who support what Kira's trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about honest citizens,\Nwho believe in their hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that by punishing evil doers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira will actually make this world\Na better place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But as for this crowd outside,\Nthey're a completely different breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They are truly despicable and stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a diversion for them.\NThey're all selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I-- I know that, but it still leaves us\Nwith the immediate problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] We'll use L's legacy\Nand the anti-Kira protestors we hired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but we only have one shot\Nwith that plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that, but I can't imagine\Na better time to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, it should be interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[mob yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's money!\N-[mob yelling and laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Money? It's so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] What? Whoa.\NThat's a lot. Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I wish I were over there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs] Humans are so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can use money to get apples,\Nso I can kind of understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,-[man 1] I grabbed it first, you bastard!\N-[man 2] Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Damn it! He's planning to use\Nall this chaos to escape into the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, he can't escape\Nfrom Demegawa's cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there, pilot! Go to the floor\Nwhere all the money's coming from!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! What are you doing, Demegawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.14,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know that you can't\Nbuy love and peace with money?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light snarls]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A literal downpour of money\Nis causing mayhem in Lower Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-[reporter] The police have arrived.\N-[Light gasps] The police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[reporter]\NThey're a welcome sight in the midst
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of what can only be called\Na full-scale riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] This is bad. At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our window of opportunity.\NWe can leave via the front exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes sense that the police would have\Nto mobilize for a riot like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Damn! Near was prepared\Nfor this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's planning to come out\Nalong with the rest of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I tell Aizawa and the others\Nto keep an eye on the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll only make me look\Nthat much more suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.47,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[reporter] The police are coming out\Nof the building. They've secured the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Where is he?\NHe's gotta be in there somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[sirens wailing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[indistinct police radio chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans] How much money\Ndo you think was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-Bet it was a lot.\N-[Ide] Matsuda, knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] I bet it was around ten million\Ndollars or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Ooh, what's that in apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-[monitor beeping]\N-[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Near!\N-Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Near] This is Near.\N-[groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We've reestablished a secure connection,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I should give you a call\Nto let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] You're safe. That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To all of you on the Task Force...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that by now, some of you\Nare starting to suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that Kira may be one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the timing of today's attack\Non our headquarters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.40,0:08:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone could blame you\Nfor having doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't suspect the second L\Nof being Kira by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you're in the wrong line of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The number I gave you\Nthe day before has been reconnected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please feel free to call anytime you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well then, I'll be waiting for your call.\N-[Aizawa sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were some strong words.\NThis guy's pretty sure of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking, and if any of you want\Nto cooperate with Near, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not particularly satisfied\Nwith the way things are going either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ideally, we should cooperate with the SPK.\NMaybe this will clear the air a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Still, it kind of feels\Nlike Near's against us, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa sighs] When I think\Nabout Deputy Director Yagami,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna suspect Light,\Neven a little bit, but… [sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Yumi] Dad?\N-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. I didn't know\Nyou were gonna be home tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. What are you still doing awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a couple of exams coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, don't push yourself\Ntoo hard, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-'Kay. You too, Dad.\N-[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ice cubes clinking]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I wouldn't be surprised\Nif one of the others contacted Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's inevitable.\NThe problem is what comes after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm too late to act,\Nsomething might happen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that I won't be able to take back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no choice but to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[beeping]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[squeals] An emergency order\Nfrom Light! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, file number three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Yes, this is Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] I'm with the Japanese Task Force.\NMy name is Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[bird chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] So, the time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do this, my safety is guaranteed,\Nand I can finally just be a normal wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what Light wants for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants me to be happy,\Njust as a woman should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I see. That's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying there were two suspects\Nin the Kira investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that the previous L detained\Nfor more than 50 days,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.60,0:11:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and they were cleared\Nbased on the 13-day rule, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Yes, but of course,\Nthat alone doesn't prove they were Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] And L was willing to release them\Nbecause of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] No. L had Deputy Director Yagami,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the chief detective at the time,\Nput on an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He was instructed to tell the suspects\Nthat they had both been found guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of being Kira and the second Kira,\Nand that they were going to be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, on the way,\Nthe Deputy Director pulled over
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and pointed a gun at the suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that he would first kill Kira,\Nthen himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] The idea was\Nthat if he were Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the suspect would've killed the chief\Nright then and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] Kira is quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have used his detainment\Nto demonstrate his innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of curiosity, did the suspect\Nvolunteer to be detained
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-as part of the investigation?\N-Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,\NLight did volunteer to be imprisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] If he did, then I'd say\Nthat settles the matter, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, who was it?\NWho were those two suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. I can't tell you that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to cooperate,\Nbut I'm still a member
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.34,0:12:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Japanese Task Force,\Nworking under L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NYour information's been quite valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.43,0:12:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially the part about Shinigami's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that enable you to see\Nother people's names.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-It was very helpful. Goodbye.\N-[hangs up]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.02,0:12:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[Rester] Will that be enough, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you have pressed\Nfor a little more information?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that all things considered,\Nhis level of cooperation is fine for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, I discovered something\Nvery important.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The person suspected of being Kira\Nis Deputy Director Yagami's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Near] It's the only possible explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else would the Deputy Director say\Nhe would kill Kira and then himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, that means the second L,\Nand the person I think is Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,can only be one man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.43,0:13:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Aizawa] Light.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something you should know.\NI phoned Near and talked to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.91,0:13:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I was the one\Nwho recommended it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did the two of you\Nend up discussing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[stammers] No, on second thought,\NI probably shouldn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not appropriate for me to ask\Nthose kinds of questions if I'm a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get me wrong.\NI wanna believe that you aren't Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've gotta be certain.\NI'm sorry to have to do this again,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wanna put you under surveillance\Nuntil we catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that goes for Misa Amane\Nas well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna search your place right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a possibility that Amane\Nmight have a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Hang on a second, Aizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] No, go right ahead.\NLook at it this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at least you can prove to everyone\Nthat I'm not sneaking around
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and contacting Misa in private, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-[keyboard clicking]\N-[Matsuda grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[door closes]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Mogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you.\NI wanna make sure too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be best for everyone\Nif Light wasn't Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but if Amane has any evidence on her\Nthat connects her with Kira, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[doorbell rings]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[both gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa] Mochi! Monchichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Light hasn't been home at all lately,\Nso I've been super bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa groans] Well, there's no way\Nshe's got the notebook hidden
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,on her dressed like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just investigating a tip\Nthat there were explosives
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,planted in L's house.\NWe think it's a prank,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but we'd like to check the rooms\Njust in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa gasps] What? How about Light?\NIs he okay? I have to call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You can't call him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] Don't worry. Light's safe\Nbut he's really busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He has some other things he has to do\Nso he's handed the investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,over to us for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it. Light loves me like crazy,\Nso he doesn't want me to call him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause that'll only make him worry\Nabout me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Search as much\Nas you like, Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't find the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Misa yawns]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, I wouldn't like all this suspicion\Nto ruin the atmosphere around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a social club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Aizawa and Mogi should do\Nas they see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. [sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for Kira's Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[jingle playing on TV]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA'S KINGDOM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] Greetings to all\Nmy fellow Kira worshippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Demegawa, the voice of our god, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold! This is the new Kira's Kingdom,\Nwhich shares its name with this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Its construction is going smoothly\Nbut will depend on the generous support...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,ARCHITECT'S CONCEPT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...of our loyal viewers.\NOnce it has been completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,let us welcome our god here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, talk about bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts] Hey, so is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. Seems like it was just a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh.\N-But just in case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,one of us is gonna stay and keep watch\Nover you for the next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Oh, that would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mogi, why don't you go back\Nto headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay on guard here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm with Monchichi instead of Mochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What's wrong? Don't you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're just not Monchichi\Nwithout your old haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not cute anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Mogi chuckles]\N-[Aizawa grumbles] Mogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[rock music playing]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We are now accepting donations,\Nstarting at the million Yen mark
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,towards the completion of Kira's Kingdom!\NSo, if you truly support Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] This sounds like a con.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ide] Yep. Just another scam\Nat this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even seem like Kira's style.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Demegawa...\NHe's just acting on his own now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If he keeps doing this, he'll end up\Npushing people away from Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need him anymore.\NBut I can't do much at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Hey, welcome back, Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] We didn't find a notebook\Nin Light or Misa's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-But still...\N-[Light] I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more than welcome to keep watch\Nover Misa and I until you're satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa] Next on the program,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it's time for me to introduce\Nthe new leaders I have chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,for Kira's Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The first gentleman is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:19:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[splutters and groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[all gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[stammering] We will unite with Kira\Nand work with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] Delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[man groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Mikami] Delete!\N-[man yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] Delete!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Demegawa panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps] Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.97,0:19:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-[heart pumping]\N-[Demegawa yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,SAKURA TV\NPLEASE STAND BY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa gasps] What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Kira kill his own supporters?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[Matsuda] Do you think it's because\Nthey're going overboard with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be a possibility.\NBut this is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[Aizawa] What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no chance\Nfor either Misa Amane or Light
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to use the notebook to kill Demegawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Mikami...\NI can definitely use him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I was right\Nto choose him for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He understands Kira's beliefs\Nand ideals perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And he knows what Kira wants\Nand doesn't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, he takes action\Nwithout needing my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I had Misa relinquish ownership\Nof the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Before she lost all her memories\Nof the notebook,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,she sent it to someone else,\Nalong with some special instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she won't be able to answer\Nany questions about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just an ordinary woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The main problem was selecting\Nthe next owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him trying to speak to Kira\Nthrough the television broadcasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was clear he worshipped Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.56,0:20:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,KIRA'S KINGDOM VIEWER SURVEY
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,DO YOU WANT TO PARTICIPATE\NIN THE NEXT SHOW? YES
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...from the bottom of his heart.\NHe would understand that he was chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,simply by receiving\Nand accepting the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,SEX: MALE\NBIRTHDATE: JUNE 7, 1982, AGE: 27
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,OCCUPATION: PROSECUTOR
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no mistake in my selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,NAME: TERU MIKAMI, YEAR OF BIRTH: 1982\NRESIDENCE: KYOTO PREFECTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru Mikami, he's more than worthy\Nof becoming the hand of Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami] Shinigami, thank you\Nfor coming to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll be able to punish evildoers\Nwith death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT IS KIRA TO YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[Mikami chuckles] God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]